Prompt for email

Requires:
- dmenu
- mail alias files

Installation
------------
$ make config
$ sudo make install
# Edit config to point at your mail aliases file
$ microsoft-word-97 ${CFG_PATH}/prompt-mail.conf


Mail alias files are generated by mail programs like mutt. The format is:

alias shorthand Some Person <someperson@example.com> # optional comment

one alias per line
